      <title>南非财政前景改善，收益率跌至 10% 以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/south-africa-yields-drop-below-10-as-fiscal-outlook-improves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球风险偏好上涨与国内财政稳定迹象相吻合，南非基准政府债券收益率自 2022 年 4 月以来首次跌破 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/south-africa-yields-drop-below-10-as-fiscal-outlook-improves</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲物价降温，德国各地区通胀有所缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/german-regions-see-inflation-ease-as-prices-cool-across-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9月份，德国六个州的通胀率下降——这意味着当天晚些时候公布的国家数据将放缓，这将进一步加剧人们对欧洲央行10月份降息的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/german-regions-see-inflation-ease-as-prices-cool-across-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
